content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 250.9 - Singular/plural use of terms

State Regulations

Any term used in the singular in these rules also
encompasses the plural of that term. For example, the terms employer or labor
organization encompasses the terms employers or labor
organizations. Notes
